<h2>Sorting through the Aftermath <small>What do all these points MEAN?</small></h2>
<ul>
    <li>After each episode, the tallies from your players are added up and added to your season total.
    <li>At the end of the season, the player with the most points wins!
    <li>Because there's no win-loss record (only total points), it is possible to not play each week and still win.  That being said, a wise person once said, 'I don't want to be the Juan Pablo of Fantasy Rose'.  Think ahead and spend wisely.</li>
</ul>
